Paper: hep-th/0205152

Date: 2002-05-15

Title: On a core instability of 't Hooft Polyakov monopoles

Authors: F.A.Bais and J.Striet

Comments: 7 pages, 4 figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B540 (2002) 319-323

We discuss a core instability of 't Hooft Polyakov monopoles in Aliceelectrodynamics type of models in which charge conjugation symmetry is gauged.The monopole may deform into a toroidal defect which carries an Alice flux anda (non-localizable) magnetic Cheshire charge.